text: Carrollton, Georgia is a city in the north west region of Georgia, about 45 miles (72 km) west of Atlanta near the Alabama state line. It is the county seat of Carroll County. The 2020 United States Census counted 26,738 people living in Carrollton. ==References== Category:Cities in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:County seats in Georgia
